When he ran out of
the cave he looked back

222
00:16:11,638 --> 00:16:13,907
and the Archangel filled
up the whole of the sky.

223
00:16:15,409 --> 00:16:18,178
Everywhere you looked there was Gabriel.

224
00:16:19,246 --> 00:16:25,052
Not just a single angelic image
but a presence, a being, a power.

225
00:16:27,020 --> 00:16:29,256
This is how the ineffable

226
00:16:29,523 --> 00:16:33,927
incomprehensible, utterly transcendent,
indescribable God

227
00:16:34,761 --> 00:16:36,430
makes itself known to us.

228
00:16:40,601 --> 00:16:44,371
This was something that really
shook him to the very core of his being.

229
00:16:44,638 --> 00:16:47,040
And he goes down from
that mountain and he is shaking.

230
00:16:47,875 --> 00:16:49,543
And I think it's, it's shock.

231
00:16:50,811 --> 00:16:52,412
Here is somebody who, who's gone

232
00:16:52,713 --> 00:16:54,481
looking for this transcendent reality

233
00:16:54,681 --> 00:16:56,984
and this transcendent reality is now

234
00:16:58,385 --> 00:16:59,019
replying.

235
00:17:02,422 --> 00:17:07,961
Muhammad was so shaken by this experience,
he feared he might be possessed.

236
00:17:09,530 --> 00:17:11,899
He ran home directly to Khadija.

237
00:17:13,166 --> 00:17:17,671
And there he flung himself into
her lap and he said cover me

238
00:17:18,005 --> 00:17:21,475
cover me, hold me,
until the terror had passed.

239
00:17:24,178 --> 00:17:27,181
Khadija was the person
who reassured him.

240
