01:50:42,543 --> 01:50:46,580
MUHAMMAD had been feeling ill.
He'd had some fever.

1554
01:50:47,381 --> 01:50:52,719
It was clear that he was in real difficulty
in terms of his health.

1555
01:50:53,420 --> 01:50:58,025
And the household seemed to be convinced that
MUHAMMAD was dying.

1556
01:50:59,126 --> 01:51:01,061
And while he was on his deathbed

1557
01:51:01,662 --> 01:51:06,533
and there were many who surrounded him,
especially his close companions and his family

1558
01:51:07,134 --> 01:51:10,537
he called for silence around him.

1559
01:51:11,004 --> 01:51:16,476
And he wanted it to be a time of quiet and
of peace and of calm.

1560
01:51:17,878 --> 01:51:21,582
Embraced by the community
he had founded in Medina and

1561
01:51:21,582 --> 01:51:24,151
cared for by his wives and companions

1562
01:51:24,451 --> 01:51:29,389
Muhammad died peacefully on
June 8th, in the year 632.

1563
01:51:31,525 --> 01:51:34,962
The news of his death shocked
his followers, especially Umar

1564
01:51:35,262 --> 01:51:38,031
who believed Muhammad
would outlive them all.

1565
01:51:38,699 --> 01:51:41,201
People began to hear
the Prophet is dead.

1566
01:51:41,568 --> 01:51:47,140
Umar went to the center square and
started to say

1567
01:51:48,041 --> 01:51:52,446
there are hypocrites and liars who are
saying that the Prophet is dead.

1568
01:51:53,680 --> 01:51:59,486
In the midst of this chaos, Abu Bakr reminded
the Muslims of a verse from the Quran

1569
01:51:59,486 --> 01:52:02,890
that had first been revealed
after the battle of Uhud

1570
01:52:03,323 --> 01:52:06,393
when they feared that Muhammad
had been killed.

1571
01:52:07,828 --> 01:52:10,497
Abu Bakr,
comes into this scene of pandemonium.

1572
01:52:10,898 --> 01:52:15,836
And he immediately, uh,
stands up and says

1573
01:52:16,103 --> 01:52:20,207
whoever worshipped Muhammad, uh,
then know that Muhammad is dead.

1574
01:52:20,574 --> 01:52:25,946
But whoever worshipped God,
know that God lives on and never dies.

1575
01:52:26,180 --> 01:52:29,650
And so, suddenly these people are
brought to their senses

1576
01:52:30,050 --> 01:52:34,988
that indeed that Muhammad is, is a man.

1577
01:52:34,988 --> 01:52:36,323
And men are mortal.

1578
01:52:36,590 --> 01:52:37,958
And, and this is his legacy.

1579
01:52:38,192 --> 01:52:43,430
He, he did everything within his power
